### Refresh the access token by providing refresh token
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/token/refresh/ HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "refresh":""
}

### Logout for any user
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/logout/ HTTP/1/1
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refresh_token":""
}
